feedback: It really is unfortunate, but the app has been problematic. I was shopping for over an hour or more, and suddenly when I'm about to checkout, all of the items in my cart are gone. I had to redo everything. The second time, I can't checkout my and complete my order because the app is showing a notification that an item is out of stock -- without telling WHICH ONE is out of stock. I had to basically guess, or figure it out myself. I ended up removing all items. I cancelled placing my order because I've now wasted at least 3 hours. I had to place my order another day. I had to calm down and recuperate for wasting my time, and I downsized my order to the most urgent ones. The only reason I'm reordering through here again is because I basically don't have another option.
